sentences: Cass Browne (born 27 September 1971 in Merton, Surrey) is an English musician and writer.
He was a member of the band The Psychotics who became Senseless Things in 1986.
Senseless Things had a couple of top 20 hits and many other singles in their nine years together, they split up in 1995.
